heme of arrangement sanctioned by the honble high court bombay the company has adjusted depreciation of rs crore and rs crore during current quarter and nine months ended st december  respectively against the amalgamation reserve     the company has invested rs crore in its subsidiary ismt enterprises luxembourg which in turn holds   investment in structo hydraulics ab sweden shab the company has given a corporate guarantee of rs  crores usd  million for loan availed by shab the net recoverable on account of supplies by the company to shab is rs  crore while shab had cash loss in the previous year and the net worth of shab is eroded the management is of the opinion that the investment made in ismt enterprises group is strategic and as a forward integration in the value chain of core business of the company and the diminution is temporary in nature as such no provision for the same is considered necessary     upon petition filed by the company regarding non implementation of energy banking agreement eba dated th may  maharashtra electricity regulatory commission merc had passed an interim order dated th may inter alia restoring the banking this order was challenged by maharashtra state electricity distribution company limited msedcl on grounds of jurisdiction before the appellate tribunal for electricity after being turned down by high court at bombay which the tribunal had rema about us the indian seamless metal tubes limited was promoted in  by a group of technocrats to produce specialized seamless tubes in india beginning with an installed capacity of  metric tons per annum ismt commenced production in  with the installation and commissioning of an assel mill in technical collaboration with mannesman demag meer of germany subsequently in  the production capacity was raised to  metric tons per annum with the addition of a second assel mill in  the indian seamless metal tubes limited promoted another company indian seamless steels and alloys ltd issal to produce all